Source: lablgtk
Section: libs
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Sven Luther <luther@debian.org>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>> 3.0.0), ocaml-3.07, libncurses5-dev, xlibs|xlib6g, liblablgl-ocaml-dev (>= 0.99-16), libgtk1.2-dev, libglib1.2-dev, gtkglarea5-dev, libglade-gnome0-dev, libgtkxmhtml-dev, libgdk-pixbuf-dev
Standards-Version: 3.6.0

Package: liblablgtk-ocaml
Architecture: any
Section: libs
Depends: ocaml-base-3.07, liblablgl-ocaml (>= 0.99-16), ${shlibs:Depends}
Conflicts: lablgtk (<< 1.2.3-2)
Replaces: lablgtk-runtime
Provides: lablgtk-runtime
Description: Runtime libraries for lablgtk.
 lablgtk contains bindings for gtk+ and ocaml. It includes gtkglarea bindings
 to be used with the OpenGL bindings of the lablgl package.
 .
 This package include only the dynamic libraries needed for running dynamic
 bytecode executables.

Package: liblablgtk-ocaml-dev
Architecture: any
Section: libdevel
Depends: liblablgtk-ocaml (= ${Source-Version}), ocaml-3.07, liblablgl-ocaml-dev (>= 0.99-16), libgtk1.2-dev, libglade-gnome-dev, libgtkxmhtml-dev
Conflicts: lablgtk
Provides: lablgtk
Replaces: lablgtk
Description: Ocaml bindings to Gtk+
 lablgtk contains bindings for gtk+ and ocaml. It includes gtkglarea bindings
 to be used with the OpenGL bindings of the lablgl package.
 .
 This package contains the developpment files of lablgtk.

